          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Charissa by: </span>
      Satan
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/570489-charissa?shelf=dystopia">dystopia</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/570489-charissa?shelf=crack">crack</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/570489-charissa?shelf=a-top-ten">a-top-ten</a>, 
