<span id="freeTextContainer2523668188570218966">An absolutely <b>terrifying true story</b> with <b>very descriptive details</b> of the horrors resulting from a highly infectious and deadly virus brought into the US from central African rain forests in the 1980&apos;s. <b>WHEW! What a nightmare!</b><p>
